Triathlete Mhlengi Gwala is our charmza for his resilient spirit even after thugs tried to saw his leg off. His  star was on the rise as he  had begun competing in international  triathlon events. By  yesterday,   R647000 had  been raised to help him with his medical expenses. People from across the world  opened their hearts and purses by donating. We wish this charmza a speedy recovery.